00053 static void rna_MovieClip_reload_update(Main *UNUSED(bmain), Scene *UNUSED(scene), PointerRNA *ptr)
00054 {
00055     MovieClip *clip = (MovieClip*)ptr->id.data;
00056 
00057     BKE_movieclip_reload(clip);
00058     DAG_id_tag_update(&clip->id, 0);
00059 }

00061 static void rna_MovieClip_size_get(PointerRNA *ptr, int *values)
00062 {
00063     MovieClip *clip = (MovieClip*)ptr->id.data;
00064 
00065     values[0] = clip->lastsize[0];
00066     values[1] = clip->lastsize[1];
00067 }

00218 static void rna_def_movieclip(BlenderRNA *brna)
00219 {
00220     StructRNA *srna;
00221     PropertyRNA *prop;
00222 
00223     static EnumPropertyItem clip_source_items[] = {
00224         {MCLIP_SRC_SEQUENCE, "SEQUENCE", 0, "Image Sequence", "Multiple image files, as a sequence"},
00225         {MCLIP_SRC_MOVIE, "MOVIE", 0, "Movie File", "Movie file"},
00226         {0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL}};
00227 
00228     srna = RNA_def_struct(brna, "MovieClip", "ID");
00229     RNA_def_struct_ui_text(srna, "MovieClip", "MovieClip datablock referencing an external movie file");
00230     RNA_def_struct_ui_icon(srna, ICON_SEQUENCE);
00231 
00232     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "filepath", PROP_STRING, PROP_FILEPATH);
00233     RNA_def_property_string_sdna(prop, NULL, "name");
00234     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "File Path", "Filename of the movie or sequence file");
00235     RNA_def_property_update(prop, NC_MOVIECLIP|ND_DISPLAY, "rna_MovieClip_reload_update");
00236 
00237     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "tracking", PROP_POINTER, PROP_NONE);
00238     RNA_def_property_struct_type(prop, "MovieTracking");
00239 
00240     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "proxy", PROP_POINTER, PROP_NONE);
00241     RNA_def_property_struct_type(prop, "MovieClipProxy");
00242 
00243     /* use proxy */
00244     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "use_proxy", PROP_BOOLEAN, PROP_NONE);
00245     RNA_def_property_boolean_sdna(prop, NULL, "flag", MCLIP_USE_PROXY);
00246     RNA_def_property_clear_flag(prop, PROP_ANIMATABLE);
00247     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Use Proxy / Timecode",
00248                              "Use a preview proxy and/or timecode index for this clip");
00249     RNA_def_property_update(prop, NC_MOVIECLIP|ND_DISPLAY, NULL);
00250 
00251     prop = RNA_def_int_vector(srna, "size" , 2 , NULL , 0, 0, "Size",
00252                               "Width and height in pixels, zero when image data cant be loaded" , 0 , 0);
00253     RNA_def_property_int_funcs(prop, "rna_MovieClip_size_get" , NULL, NULL);
00254     RNA_def_property_clear_flag(prop, PROP_EDITABLE);
00255 
00256     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "display_aspect", PROP_FLOAT, PROP_XYZ);
00257     RNA_def_property_float_sdna(prop, NULL, "aspx");
00258     RNA_def_property_array(prop, 2);
00259     RNA_def_property_range(prop, 0.1f, 5000.0f);
00260     RNA_def_property_ui_range(prop, 0.1f, 5000.0f, 1, 2);
00261     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Display Aspect", "Display Aspect for this clip, does not affect rendering");
00262     RNA_def_property_update(prop, NC_MOVIECLIP|ND_DISPLAY, NULL);
00263 
00264     /* source */
00265     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "source", PROP_ENUM, PROP_NONE);
00266     RNA_def_property_enum_items(prop, clip_source_items);
00267     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Source", "Where the clip comes from");
00268     RNA_def_property_clear_flag(prop, PROP_EDITABLE);
00269 
00270     /* custom proxy directory */
00271     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "use_proxy_custom_directory", PROP_BOOLEAN, PROP_NONE);
00272     RNA_def_property_boolean_sdna(prop, NULL, "flag", MCLIP_USE_PROXY_CUSTOM_DIR);
00273     RNA_def_property_clear_flag(prop, PROP_ANIMATABLE);
00274     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Proxy Custom Directory",
00275                              "Create proxy images in a custom directory (default is movie location)");
00276     RNA_def_property_update(prop, NC_MOVIECLIP|ND_DISPLAY, "rna_MovieClip_reload_update");
00277 
00278     /* grease pencil */
00279     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "grease_pencil", PROP_POINTER, PROP_NONE);
00280     RNA_def_property_pointer_sdna(prop, NULL, "gpd");
00281     RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_EDITABLE);
00282     RNA_def_property_struct_type(prop, "GreasePencil");
00283     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Grease Pencil", "Grease pencil data for this movie clip");
00284 }
